---
title: Double Herby Chicken & Brown Butter Sauce with Potato Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: The garlicky, buttery sauce is the star of this meal, drizzled over tender chicken to add juiciness and flavour. Let’s add a creamy mash to help soak up the last of that sauce, and some steamed veggies to cut through all that richness. Bon appétit!

*We’ve replaced the pea pods in this recipe with green beans due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67a57394f47ee53eafcd825c-153133d7.jpeg
